des:
Amazon Alexa and the MIRATI HOME products work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off the device. 
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your MIRATI HOME products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "MIRATI HOME" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one MIRATI HOME account in our "MIRATI HOME" app;
(3). You need to have some MIRATI HOME devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our “MIRATI HOME" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "MIRATI HOME" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "MIRATI HOME" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "MIRATI HOME", and you'll be navigated to MIRATI HOME login page;
(9). Input your MIRATI HOME account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:

“Alexa, turn on light"
“Alexa, turn of light"
